        <br>
        <p><strong>How can you use Float?</strong></p>
        <ul>
            <li>See your team's projects</li>
            <li>Track your assigned tasks</li>
            <li>Get notified when work changes</li>
            <li>Manage your availability and plan time off</li>
            <li>Log your timesheets (in just a few taps!)</li>
        </ul>
        <br>
        <a href="{{ url }}" class="btn">Let's log in</a>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
